20in%20strong%20winds%20as%20many%20homes%20burned%20on%20January%207.%3Cp%3EDavid%20McNew%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20see%20that%20there%20was%20no%20one%20there%20except%20for%20one%20firetruck.%20It%20was%20like%20a%20wasteland.%20I%20couldn't%20believe%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20saw%20this%20pickup%20truck%20on%20fire%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%2C%20and%20I%20knew%2C%20I%20had%20the%20feeling%20then%2C%20that%20my%20house%20was%20gone%20and%20I%20couldn't%20go%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222732f38d-2685-4d15-962b-c895af7a7103%5C%22%3E'This%20was%20our%20oasis'%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20there%20was%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20partner%2C%20Jamie%2C%20and%20I%20bought%20the%20house%20in%202008%20for%20%24760%2C000%20and%20it%20was%20now%20worth%20about%20%241.6%20million.%20When%20it%20was%20built%20in%201909%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20main%20houses%20there%20in%20Altadena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20home%20was%20our%20oasis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20beautiful%20backyard%2C%20plants%2C%20a%20hot%20tub.%20We%20were%20doing%20gardening%20and%20renovations.%20We%20took%20in%20rescue%20dogs%20that%20needed%20help%20along%20the%20way%20because%20we%20had%20a%20half-acre.%20It%20was%20our%20sanctuary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20when%20Jamie%20got%20diagnosed%20with%20terminal%20cancer%20in%202010%2C%20she%20got%20sick%20pretty%20quickly%2C%20and%20the%20renovations%20stopped.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20my%20everything%2C%20and%20then%20when%20she%20died%2C%20that%20house%20was%20my%20connection%20to%20her%20and%20my%20way%20of%20honoring%20her%20by%20continuing%20the%20renovations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20back%20of%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ae3562fcded5e9073cf81%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVerreault%20and%20her%20partner%20committed%20to%20renovating%20the%20old%20house%2C%20the%20back%20of%20which%20is%20seen%20here.%3Cp%3ESue%20Verreault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20behind%2C%20like%20my%20grandmother's%20perfume%20that%20smelled%20like%20her%2C%20and%20especially%20things%20of%20Jamie's%20that%20I%20cherish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20her%20clothes.%20I%20had%20her%20ashes%20in%20a%20necklace%20and%20partially%20spread%20in%20our%20backyard.%20That's%20gone.%20But%20she's%20in%20my%20heart.%20She'll%20always%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Saturday%2C%20my%20friends%20took%20me%20to%20see%20what%20was%20left%20of%20my%20house%2C%20and%20if%20there%20was%20anything%20we%20could%20salvage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20looked%20at%20my%20house%2C%20and%20I%20climbed%20my%20concrete%20stairs%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20the%20devastation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0everything%20gone%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20I%20saw%20my%20fireplace%20standing%2C%20I%20collapsed%20to%20the%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22image%20of%20smiling%20couple%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678ae37610c98eace9130089%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22728%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVerreault%20and%20her%20partner%20Jamie%2C%20left.%3Cp%3ESue%20Verreault%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20felt%20desperation.%20I%20felt%20this%20deep%2C%20deep%2C%20deep%2C%20deep%20loss.%20And%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20thought%20of%20was%20Jamie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20breathe.%20I%20was%20having%20a%20panic%20attack%2C%20and%20I%20was%20throwing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20put%20my%20savings%20into%20that%20house.%20That%20was%20my%20retirement.%20I%20put%20everything%20into%20that%20house.%20And%20because%20of%20all%20the%20upgrades%20I%20did%2C%20my%20mortgage%20payments%20are%20over%20%244%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20to%20pay%20for%