er.com%2F67853ac250dfd88e193e0fd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20views%20inside%20the%20reporter's%20room.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20roomette%20sleeps%20up%20to%20two%20people.%20During%20the%20day%2C%20the%20room%20was%20set%20up%20with%20two%20seats%2C%20which%20reclined%20to%20form%20the%20lower%20bunk.%20The%20upper%20bunk%20could%20be%20pulled%20down%20to%20reveal%20the%20cot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%20to%20one%20of%20the%20chairs%2C%20there%20was%20a%20shelf%20below%20a%20tall%20mirror.%20There%20were%20multiple%20hooks%20around%20the%20room%20that%20I%20used%20for%20jackets%20and%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20tell%20the%20seats%20were%20new.%20They%20were%20wide%20and%20cushy%20with%20no%20signs%20of%20wear.%20But%20just%20to%20make%20sure%2C%20I%20asked%20Magliari%20how%20a%20passenger%20could%20tell%20if%20they%20were%20in%20an%20updated%20sleeper%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoing%20away%20with%20the%20blue%20fabric%20is%20the%20biggest%20giveaway%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20gray%2C%20vinyl%20seating%2C%20then%20you%20know%20that%20you%20are%20in%20a%20fresh%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMagliari%20added%20that%20the%20new%20seat%20cushions%20and%20upholstery%20provide%20more%20lumbar%20support%20than%20the%20older%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20sides%20of%20each%20headrest%20contained%20room%20controls.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20close-ups%20on%20room%20controls%20in%20an%20Amtrak%20sleeper%20cabin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67853b5e8951662c9f1fd859%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoom%20controls%20in%20the%20roomette.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20lighting%2C%20speaker%20volume%2C%20and%20temperature%20controls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20one%20outlet%20and%20a%20call%20button%20for%20the%20attendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBetween%20the%20chairs%2C%20a%20pullout%20table%20had%20two%20foldout%20leaves%20for%20extra%20space.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20a%20gray%20table%20with%20two%20leaves%20folded%20out%20inside%20a%20train%20car%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67853b3150dfd88e193e0ff4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20pullout%20table%20folded%20out.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20cupholders%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20table%20%E2%80%94%20each%20holding%20a%20complimentary%20water%20bottle.%20However%2C%20the%20holders%20were%20too%20shallow%20to%20contain%20the%20bottles%20when%20the%20train%20shook%2C%20causing%20them%20to%20fall%20over%20during%20turbulent%20stretches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cupholder%20size%20is%20a%20challenge%20we've%20faced.%20Beverage%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20change%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Magliari%20told%20BI%2C%20alluding%20to%20the%20rise%20of%20brands%20expanding%20circumference%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-stanley-cup-wedding-day-harry-potter-books-quencher-collection-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStanley%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Yeti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20thin%20closet%20stood%20above%20a%20small%20trash%20can%20next%20to%20one%20seat.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20skinny%20closet%20and%20a%20small%20trash%20can%20in%20an%20Amtrak%20roomette%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67853afe8951662c9f1fd833%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmenities%20inside%20the%20