0Belt%20markets%20are%20poised%20to%20benefit%20the%20most%20from%20this%20trend.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%205%20markets%20that%20are%20ripe%20for%20a%20so-called%20silver%20tsunami.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20what's%20been%20dubbed%20a%20silver%20tsunami%2C%20there's%20an%20%2484%20trillion%20generational%20wealth%20transfer%20that's%20slated%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20next%20two%20decades%20as%20boomers%20age%20and%20pass%20on%20their%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20seriously%20shake%20up%20a%20housing%20market%20where%20home%20ownership%20is%20heavily%20skewed%20toward%20older%20Americans.%20Boomers%2C%20who%20comprise%2020%25%20of%20the%20overall%20US%20population%2C%20owned%2036%25%20of%20all%20homes%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Freddie%20Mac.%20They're%20also%20sitting%20on%20over%20%2417%20trillion%2C%20or%20roughly%20half%2C%20of%20the%20total%20home%20equity%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20silver%20tsunami%20might%20not%20be%20a%20silver%20bullet%20for%20the%20housing%20crisis%20at%20a%20national%20level%2C%20according%20to%20Orphe%20Divougny%2C%20a%20senior%20economist%20at%20Zillow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20certain%20markets%20throughout%20the%20country%20have%20a%20particularly%20high%20concentration%20of%20empty-nest%20homes%2C%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20come%20on%20to%20the%20market%20as%20their%20boomer%20owners%20either%20downsize%20or%20pass%20away%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20but%20have%20been%20discouraged%20by%20the%20lack%20of%20supply%20on%20the%20market%2C%20these%20areas%20could%20provide%20an%20easier%20entry%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoomer-heavy%20metro%20areas%20don't%20have%20much%20overlap%20with%20the%20expensive%20markets%20popular%20with%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20such%20as%20San%20Jose%2C%20Austin%2C%20and%20Denver%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%20That%20means%20inventory%20in%20those%20hot%20spots%20won't%20see%20much%20of%20a%20boost%20from%20empty-nester%20houses%20coming%20onto%20the%20market.%20Rather%2C%20many%20of%20the%20markets%20that%20have%20a%20high%20concentration%20of%20empty-nest%20households%20are%20located%20in%20the%20Rust%20Belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20are%20proving%20that%20they're%20increasingly%20willing%20to%20relocate%20out%20of%20expensive%20metro%20areas%20and%20seek%20affordability%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20flexibility%20of%20remote%20and%20hybrid%20work.%20In%20fact%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20recent%20trend%20of%20younger%20Americans%20moving%20out%20of%20cities%20and%20into%20suburban%20or%20exurban%20communities.%20Some%20are%20going%20even%20further%20into%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20homeowners%20willing%20to%20look%20outside%20the%20popular%20housing%20markets%2C%20there%20are%20deals%20to%20be%20found%20where%20the%20boomers%20are%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20these%20homes%20hit%20the%20market%20as%20owners%20downsize%20or%20otherwise%20move%20on%2C%20that%20extra%20supply%20should%20benefit%20buyers%2C%26quot%3B%20Divougny%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EListed%20below%20are%20the%20top%20five%20housing%20markets%20that'll%20benefit%20from%20the%20silver%20tsunami%20and%20the%20percentage%20of%20empty-nest%20households%20in%20each%2C%20according%20to%20Zillow.%20For%20context%2C%20the%20average%20empty-nester%20share%20of%20households%20in%202022%20nationwide%20was%2016%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b701fc26-38af-4646-913f-3e9b12699615%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5%20housing%20markets%20ripe%20for%20a%20silver%20tsunami%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPittsburgh%2C%20PA%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20shot%20of%20large%20Victorian%20houses%20in%20Friendship%2C%20a%20neighborhood%20in%20the%20East%20End%20of%20Pittsburgh%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6762d8920a6d56a4f9c1c842%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D