0will%20be%20heard%20on%20Monday.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20sending%20you%20to%20judicial%20custody.%20Your%20punishment%20will%20be%20pronounced%20on%20Monday.%20I%20have%20fixed%20the%20time%20at%2012%3A30%20pm%20to%20hear.%20Then%20I%20will%20pronounce%20the%20punishment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20criticised%20some%20activities%20of%20the%20police%20authorities%20and%20hospital%20authorities%20which%20came%20out%20in%20the%20evidence.%20Activities%20of%20the%20head%20of%20department%2C%20medical%20superintendent%20cum%20vice-principal%20(MSVP)%20and%20principal%20created%20some%20confusion%20and%20that%20has%20been%20criticised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20was%20pronounced%20nearly%20two%20months%20after%20the%20in-camera%20trial%20commenced%20in%20November%20last%20year%20and%20over%20160%20days%20after%20the%20heinous%20crime%20was%20committed%20on%20August%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crime%20led%20to%20nationwide%20outrage%20and%20protests%20by%20junior%20doctors%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20the%20victim%20and%20stronger%20security%20arrangements%20in%20state-run%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mamata%20Banerjee-led%20Trinamool%20Congress%20government%20in%20West%20Bengal%20also%20came%20under%20fire%20from%20doctors%20and%20opposition%20parties%20for%20its%20alleged%20mishandling%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737196080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fao239mt_sanjay_625x300_18_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fim-being-framed-kolkata-rape-murder-convict-to-court-after-verdict-7502486%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sanjay%20Roy%2C%20the%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20gruesome%20rape%20and%20murder%20case%20of%20a%20trainee%20doctor%20at%20the%20state-run%20RG%20Kar%20hospital%2C%20has%20been%20found%20guilty%20by%20a%20