%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-not-happy-about-trump-ukraine-peace-plans-says-lavrov-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20touted%20by%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%2C%20predicated%20on%20delaying%20Ukraine's%20admission%20to%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-01-16%2Ftrump-team-readies-oil-sanctions-plan-for-russia-deal-iran-squeeze%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20the%20next%20administration%20is%20discussing%20two%20approaches.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20White%20House%20may%20recommend%20good-faith%20measures%20to%20help%20Russia's%20oil%20producers%20if%20a%20peace%20deal%20looks%20likely.%20Alternatively%2C%20Trump%20might%20choose%20to%20amplify%20sanctions%20pressure%20with%20deeper%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20option%20would%20build%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-ukraine-war-recession-outlook-inflation-sanctions-banks-rates-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esanctions%20regime%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20started%20and%20grew%20under%20Biden.%20Since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20war%20in%202022%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20progressively%20tightened%20the%20screws%20on%20Russia's%20oil%20industry%2C%20a%20sector%20that%20is%20vital%20to%20the%20country's%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20has%20repeatedly%20stated%20that%20a%20top%20priority%20in%20his%20second%20term%20will%20be%20to%20quickly%20negotiate%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20Karoline%20Leavitt%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20president-elect's%20transition%20team%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20plans%20for%20more%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20ahead%20of%20Biden's%20departure%2C%20Washington%20unleashed%20an%20%3Ca%20href