%2Fi.insider.com%2F678a8304ae09223df2ba7038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20iStock%3B%20Rebecca%20Zisser%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20has%20indicated%20he%20wants%20to%20put%20tariffs%20in%20place%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrade%20policy%20experts%20told%20BI%20he%20could%20do%20so%20using%20a%20national%20emergency%20trade%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20it'll%20take%20time%20for%20tariffs%20to%20actually%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20Americans%20could%20see%20price%20increases%20quickly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-technology-clothes-appliances-furniture-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20tariffs%20are%20looming%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20about%20to%20take%20office%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Americans%20could%20see%20the%20impacts%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20Trump%20has%20suggested%20a%20range%20of%20tariff%20proposals%20related%20to%20key%20trading%20partners%20with%20the%20US%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-goods-are-imported-china-mexico-canada-trump-tariff-trade-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-threats-top-imports-brics-china-trade-prices-dollar-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20BRICS%20nations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Trump's%20largest%20target%20has%20been%20China%2C%20with%20a%2060%25%20tariff%20proposal%2C%20along%20with%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20not%20specified%20which%20authorities%20he%20will%20use%20for%20tariff%20implementation%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20that%20he%20could%20choose%20to%20roll%20them%20out%20at%20a%20smaller%20scale%20than%20he%20had%20initially%20proposed.%20However%2C%20he%20has%20previously%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20begin%20the%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-higher-inflation-fed-interest-rates-taxes-mortgage-rates-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eputting%20tariffs%20in%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20first%20day%20in%20office%2C%20saying%20that%20he'll%20use%20his%20executive%20authority%20to%20roll%20them%20out%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20his%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20January%2020th%2C%20as%20one%20of%20my%20many%20first%20Executive%20Orders%2C%20I%20will%20sign%20all%20necessary%20documents%20to%20charge%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20a%2025%25%20Tariff%20on%20ALL%20products%20coming%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20its%20ridiculous%20Open%20Borders%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20wrote%20in%20a%20November%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthsocial.com%2F%40realDonaldTrump%2Fposts%2F113546215051155542%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-01-13%2Ftrump-team-studies-gradual-tariff-hikes-under-emergency-powers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20suggested%20that%20Trump%20might%20use%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20a%20president%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20national%20emergency.%20Some%20trade%20policy%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Trump%20could%20use%20emergency%20powers%20to%20begin%20rolling%20out%20his%20tariff%20plans%20on%20day%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they%20would%20take%20time%20to%20actually%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20Americans%20could%20still%20quickly%20begin%20to%20see%20price%20increases%20on%20impacted%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInu%20Manak%2C%20a%20trade%20policy%20fellow%20at%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20US%20would%20likely%20see%20an%20economic%20impact%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20soon%26quot%3B%20after%20Trump%20makes%20a%20tariff%20announcement%20because%20markets%20could%20react%20to%20it%20before%20any%20plans%20actually%20go%20into%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20also%20have%20firms%20shift%20a%20lot%20of%20their%20production%20where%20they%20can%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20stockpile%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20move%20things%20around%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20raise%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20Manak%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20tariff%20could%20actually%20take%20place%20before%20the%20tariffs%20are%20even%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20previously%20denied%20that%20his%20tariff%20plans%20will%20raise%20prices%20for%20Americans.%20Brian%20Hughes%2C%20a%20Trump-Vance%20transition%20spokesperson%2C%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20Trump%20%26quot%3Bhas%20promised%20tariff%20policies%20that%20protect%20the%20American%20manufacturers%20and%20working%20men%20and%20women%20from%20the%20unfair%20practices%20of%20foreign%20companies%20and%20foreign%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20he%20did%20in%20his%20first%20term%2C%20he%20will%20implement%20economic%20and%20trade%20policies%20to%20make%20life%20affordable%20and%20more%20prosperous%20for%20our%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Hughes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223e429007-968b-4209-bddc-f73df40a247d%5C%22%3EHow%20Trump%20can%20roll%20out%20his%20tariffs%20on%20day%20one%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20range%20of%20existing%20avenues%20within%20federal%20trade%20law%20that%20Trump%20could%20pursue%20to%20implement%20his%20tariffs.%20One%20route%20%E2%80%94%20which%20has%20never%20been%20used%20before%20for%20tariff%20implementation%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0is%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManak%20said%20that%20under%20this%20act%2C%20all%20Trump%20would%20have%20to%20do%20is%20declare%20a%20threat%20outside%20the%20US%20that%20threatens%20national%20security%2C%20foreign%20policy%2C%20or%20the%20economy.%20Once%20he%20declares%20his%20intent%20to%20use%20tariffs%20to%20address%20that%20threat%2C%20Congress%20would%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20push%20back%20on%20the%20executive%20order%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Manak%20said%20that's%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20under%20a%20Republican-controlled%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20under%20that%20law%2C%20it%20would%20still%20take%20some%20time%20for%20tariffs%20to%20come%20into%20effect.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20moving%20parts.%20It's%20not%20like%20the%20tariffs%20would%20be%20charged%20on%20the%20first%20day%20that%20he%20comes%20into%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Manak%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there's%20also%20the%20possibility%20of%20legal%20challenges%20from%20companies%20who%20the%20tariffs%20would%20impact.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20the%20meantime%2C%20we'll%20probably%20have%20some%20sort%20of%20implementation%20occur%20in%20the%20first%20few%20months%20that%20he's%20in%20office%20if%20he%20chooses%20to%20do%20that%20route.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20have%20already%20introduced%20legislation%20to%20prevent%20Trump%20from%20implementing%20tariffs%20using%20IEEPA.%20On%20January%2015%2C%20Reps.%20Suzan%20DelBene%20and%20Don%20Beyer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdelbene.house.gov%2Fnews%2Fdocumentsingle.aspx%3FDocumentID%3D4013%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintroduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Prevent%20Tariff%20Abuse%20Act%2C%20which%20would%20prohibit%20Trump%20from%20imposing%20tariffs%20using%20IEEPA%20without%20congressional%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20outrageous%20that%20without%20congressional%20approval%2C%20one%20of%20President%20Trump's%20first%20actions%20upon%20taking%20office%20could%20be%20creating%20what%20is%20effectively%20a%20nationwide%20sales%20tax%20on%20foreign%20goods%20that%20saddles%20working%20families%20with%20higher%20prices%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20the%20gas%20pump%2C%20and%20the%20pharmacy%20counter%2C%26quot%3B%20DelBene%20told%20reporters%20on%20a%20press%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Wolff%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Peterson%20Institute%20for%20International%20Economics%20and%20former%20deputy%20director-general%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20along%20with%20IEEPA%2C%20he%20could%20see%20two%20other%20trade%20laws%20%E2%80%94%20Section%20338%20of%20the%20Tariff%20Act%20and%20Section%20301%20of%20the%20Trade%20Act%20%E2%80%94%20as%20viable%20alternatives%20Trump%20could%20use%20to%20implement%20tariffs.%20They%20would%20allow%20Trump%20to%20impose%20tariffs%20if%20finds%20there%20are%20unfair%20trade%20practices%20from%20foreign%20countries.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20routes%20are%20available%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Wolff%20said%20it's%20likely%20Trump%20is%20threatening%20tariffs%20as%20a%20negotiation%20tactic%20to%20achieve%20policy%20goals%2C%20and%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20tariffs%20may%20end%20up%20not%20being%20as%20broad%20as%20initially%20proposed.%20Trump%20said%20when%20proposing%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20that%20he%20wanted%20the%20countries%20to%20strengthen%20border%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20guess%20is%20he%20favors%20using%20tariffs%20as%20a%20hammer%20to%20get%20results%20that%20he%20likes%2C%26quot%3B%20Wolff%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221fee7c2a-fee0-4efb-a438-12b71a815248%5C%22%3EThe%20impact%20of%20tariffs%20on%20Americans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20inflation%20did%20not%20increase%20significantly%20under%20the%20tariffs%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20some%20economists%20and%20trade%20experts%20expect%20the%20broader%20scope%20of%20Trump's%20proposals%20this%20time%20around%20to%20have%20a%20greater%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMary%20Lovely%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Peterson%20Institute%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20she%20expects%20consumers%20will%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-how-shoppers-and-small-businesses-are-stocking-up-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20impact%20of%20proposed%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Brather%20quickly%20this%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20businesses%20deciding%20whether%20they're%20going%20to%20absorb%20those%20extra%20costs%20or%20they're%20going%20to%20pass%20them%20through%20to%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20Lovely%20said.%20%26quot%3BGiven%20that%20consumer%20spending%20has%20been%20fairly%20buoyant%20and%20that%20the%20economy%20is%20doing%20well%2C%20we%20would%20expect%20them%20to%20pass%20a%20lot%20of%20it%20through%20to%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20businesses%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-trump-tariffs-inflation-goods-getting-more-expensive-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealready%20warned%20of%20price%20increases%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20Trump%20implement%20broad%20tariffs.%20Walmart%20CFO%20John%20David%20Rainey%20told%20CNBC%20in%20November%20that%20if%20Trump's%20tariff%20proposals%20go%20into%20effect%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere%20probably%20will%20be%20cases%20where%20prices%20will%20go%20up%20for%20consumers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManak%20said%20that%20some%20businesses%20might%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etry%20to%20stockpile%20products%20before%20the%20tariffs%20are%20implemented%2C%20and%20larger%20firms%20would%20have%20an%20advantage%20because%20they%20likely%20have%20more%20warehouses%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20move%20things%20around%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20smaller%20firms%20and%20small%20businesses%2C%20midsize%20businesses%2C%20it's%20much%20more%20challenging%2C%26quot%3B%20Manak%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20for%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20folks%2C%20it%20might%20make%20sense%20for%20them%20just%20to%20increase%20prices%20right%20away%20because%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20make%20up%20that%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-trade-plans-consumer-goods-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737190921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F678a8304ae09223df2ba7038%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-trade-plans-consumer-goods-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It'll%20take%20time%20for%20Trump's%20tariffs%20to%20be%20implemented%2C%20but%20goods%20could%20still%20start%20getting%20more%20expensive%20in%20the%20meantime.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-trump-tariffs-will-impact-prices-trade-plans-consumer-goods-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22So%20many%20young%20people%20with%20colon%20cancer%20have%20clean%20diets.%20What%20gives%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20collage%20with%20foods%20and%20xray.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67619ad16c531c315b88bff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EIncreasingly%2C%20young%20people%20with%20clean%20diets%20and%20healthy%20lifestyles%20are%20getting%20colon%20cancer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDoctors%20say%20diet%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20the%20rising%20risk%2C%20but%20doesn't%20tell%20the%20whole%20story.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20are%20learning%20more%20about%20ways%20micropla