ump%20had%20signed%20just%20one%20executive%20order%2C%20which%20targeted%20Obamacare.%20But%20this%20time%20around%2C%20he%20has%20promised%20quite%20a%20few%20orders.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMass%20deportation%20program%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20immigration%20plans%20are%20a%20key%20aspect%20of%20his%20day-one%20agenda.%20He%20has%20vowed%20to%20begin%20a%20mass%20deportation%20program%2C%20targeting%20undocumented%20migrants.%20%26quot%3BOn%20day%20one%2C%20I%20will%20launch%20the%20largest%20deportation%20program%20in%20American%20history%20to%20get%20the%20criminals%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20This%20promise%20has%20raised%20concerns%20among%20immigration%20advocates%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20such%20a%20program%20would%20be%20logistically%20challenging%20and%20potentially%20harmful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnd%20birthright%20citizenship%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%2C%20a%20right%20granted%20to%20anyone%20born%20in%20the%20United%20States%20under%20the%2014th%20Amendment.%20This%20move%20would%20likely%20face%20significant%20legal%20and%20logistical%20challenges.%20When%20asked%20if%20he%20plans%20to%20end%20birthright%20citizenship%20on%20day%20one%2C%20Trump%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BAbsolutely.%26quot%3B%20Additionally%2C%20Trump%20has%20vowed%20to%20terminate%20every%20open-borders%20policy%20of%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20he%20has%20even%20said%20that%20he%20will%20%26quot%3Buse%20Title%2042%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20public%20health%20law%20that%20allows%20for%20faster%20deportation%20of%20migrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPardon%20Capitol%20Hill%20rioters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20issue%20of%20pardons%2C%20Trump%20has%20promised%20to%20pardon%20defendants%20convicted%20for%20their%20role%20in%20the%20January%206%2C%202021%2C%20attack%20on%20the%20US%20Capitol.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20looking%20first%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20his%20timeline%20for%20pardons.%20He%20has%20also%20stated%20that%20he%20would%20consider%20pardoning%20defendants%20charged%20with%20violent%20crimes%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20at%20it.%26quot%3B%20This%20move%20has%20sparked%20controversy%2C%20with%20many%20arguing%20that%20pardoning%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20January%206%20attack%20would%20undermine%20the%20rule%20of%20law.%20Furthermore%2C%20he%20told%20Time%20magazine%2C%20%26quot%3BI'll%20be%20looking%20at%20J6%20early%20on%2C%20maybe%20the%20first%20nine%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnding%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20foreign%20policy%2C%20Trump%20has%20made%20the%20bold%20claim%20that%20he%20can%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20taking%20office%2C%20or%20even%20before.%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20war%20that's%20dying%20to%20be%20settled.%20I%20will%20get%20it%20settled%20before%20I%20even%20become%20president%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20during%20a%20debate%20with%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20%5BUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%5D%20Zelenskyy%20very%20well%2C%20and%20I%20know%20%5BRussian%20President%20Vladimir%5D%20Putin%20very%20well.%20I%20have%20a%20good%20relationship%20and%20they%20respect%20your%20president%2C%20OK%2C%20they%20respect%20me.%20They%20don't%20respect%20Biden%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETariff%20implementation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20implement%20tariffs%20on%20products%20imported%20from%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%2C%20two%20of%20America's%20biggest%20trading%20partners.%20This%20move%20has%20raised%20concerns%20among%20economists%2C%20who%20argue%20that%20such%20tariffs%20could%20have%20drastic%20and%20harmful%20effects%20on%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20January%2020th%2C%20as%20one%20of%20my%20many%20first%20Executive%20Orders%2C%20I%20will%20sign%20all%20necessary%20documents%20to%20charge%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20a%2025%25%20Tariff%20on%20ALL%20products%20coming%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20its%20ridiculous%20Open%20Borders%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20Truth%20Social%20on%20Nov.%2025.%20He%20even%20referred%20to%20the%20word%20tariff%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20most%20beautiful%20word%20in%20the%20entire%20dictionary%20of%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnd%20Biden's%20'electric%20vehicle%20mandate'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20economic%20issues%2C%20Trump%20has%20vowed%20to%20cancel%20the%20electric%20vehicle%20%26quot%3Bmandate%26quot%3B%20implemented%20by%20the%20Biden%20administration.%20%26quot%3BThe%20day%20I%20take%20office%2C%20I%20will%20cancel%20Crooked%20Joe's%20electric%20vehicle%20mandate%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20during%20a%20campaign%20event%20in%20Houston.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mandate%20Trump%20has%20been%20speaking%20about%20is%20an%20order%20Biden%20signed%20setting%20a%20national%20goal%20aiming%20for%2050%25%20of%20new%20cars%20and%20trucks%20sold%20by%202030%20to%20be%20zero-emission.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20Environmental%20Protection%20Agency%20finalised%20the%20tailpipe%20emission%20limits%20and%20electric%20vehicles%20were%20expected%20to%20help%20reach%20the%20goals.%20Trump%20has%20referred%20to%20this%20as%20%26quot%3Belectric%20vehicle%20mandates%26quot%3B%2C%20although%20no%20one%20is%20required%20to%20buy%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrill%2C%20drill%2C%20drill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20increase%20oil%20drilling%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BDrill%2C%20drill%2C%20drill%26quot%3B%20during%20a%20town%20hall%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%20host%20S