rsy%20after%20making%20insensitive%20remarks%20regarding%20the%20attack%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsaif-ali-khan-attack-urvashi-rautela-issues-apology-to-the-actor-for-her-insensitive-and-ignorant-remarks-was-caught-up-in-the-excitement-of-my-gifts-7500579%5C%22%3ESaif%20Ali%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20actor%20shared%20an%20apology%20post%20on%20social%20media%2C%20only%20to%20delete%20it%20shortly%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Internet%20wasted%20no%20time%20in%20reacting%2C%20with%20users%20calling%20out%20her%20actions.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BApologising%20and%20deleting%3F%20Is%20this%20a%20joke%20or%20a%20publicity%20stunt%3F%26quot%3B%20Another%20one%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20she's%20just%20trying%20to%20stay%20relevant.%20This%20doesn't%20feel%20like%20an%20apology.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20apologised%2C%20then%20deleted%20it%3F%20That%20just%20makes%20everything%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20comment%20read.%20While%20a%20fan%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20apologise%20if%20you're%20just%20going%20to%20take%20it%20down%3F%20Looks%20like%20she's%20not%20even%20taking%20her%20own%20apology%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20post%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20embarrassing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EICYDK%3A%20In%20an%20interview%20with%20ANI%2C%20Urvashi%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20stabbing%20incident%20at%20Saif's%20Mumbai%20residence.%20While%20she%20voiced%20her%20concern%20for%20the%20actor%2C%20her%20comment%20about%20her%20jewellery%20drew%20ire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate.%20Now%20Daaku%20Maharaaj%20has%20crossed%20Rs%20105%20crore%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20and%20my%20mother%20gifted%20me%20this%20diamond-studded%20Rolex%2C%20while%20my%20father%20gifted%20me%20this%20mini%20watch%20on%20my%20finger%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20feel%20confident%20wearing%20it%20outside%2