0he%20wanted%20to%20solve%20sustainably.%20With%20his%20curiosity%20piqued%20and%20his%20heart%20set%20on%20helping%2C%20he%20thought%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20upcycling%20textile%20waste%2C%20a%20serious%20environmental%20issue%2C%20and%20using%20it%20to%20create%20school%20bags%20that%20would%20be%20eco-friendly%20and%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Threads4Good%20came%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20moment%20that%20stirred%20the%20idea%20for%20%E2%80%98Threads4Good%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20initiative%20founded%20on%20empathy%20and%20the%20belief%20that%20communities%20can%20unite%20to%20solve%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20pressing%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20knew%20that%20this%20was%20not%20a%20task%20he%20could%20tackle%20alone%20and%20understood%20the%20importance%20of%20collaboration.%20%E2%80%9CI%20needed%20help%2C%20but%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20to%20start.%20I%20turned%20to%20my%20connections%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20response%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%2C%20I%20had%20a%20group%20of%20like-minded%20volunteers%20from%20all%20over%20India%2C%20eager%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-09-18-at-1.14.21-PM-1_11zon-1736083535.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tejas%20and%20his%20team%20conduct%20regular%20quality%20checks%20to%20ensure%20the%20bags%20are%20durable%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2